\begin{verbatim}
SmoothRect(F, tstart, tr, duration)
\end{verbatim}
Struct to define a smooth rectangular excitation signal

\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{F::Real}: Amplitude of the force [N]


\item \texttt{tstart::Real}: Starting time of the excitation [s]


\item \texttt{duration::Real}: Duration of the excitation [s]


